<details>
	<summary>Javascript code sample to schedule the CSS addition for pink day</summary>
	<p>The following script adds the CSS class only on April 10, 2019 based on local time.</p>
<pre><code>( function( d ) {
"use strict";

var t = new Date(),
	msT = t.getTime(),
	s = new Date( 2019, 3, 10, 0, 1 ),
	e = new Date( 2019, 3, 10, 23, 59 );

if ( s.getTime() &lt; msT && msT &lt; e.getTime() ) {
	d.getElementsByTagName( "html" )[ 0 ].classList.add ("pnkDy-theme", "experimental");
}

} )( document );</code></pre>
</details>

